  "body": "Introduced by https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15204\r\ncc: @alwx \r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Open a chat with a significant amount of messages.\r\n2. Perform a quick scroll to the top by swiping upwards rapidly.\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\nThe top bar of the screen flashes briefly during the quick scroll action\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/268fcce1-90d2-4e5a-be8a-c6a4f13a16e9\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nThe top bar remains stable and does not flash during the quick scroll action\r\n\r\n### Devices:\r\n- iPhone 11 Pro max, IOS 16",
